**********************
* sandbox name collisions
**********************
Create a new sandboxs named xterm, and restart firetools - the new sandbox replaces the existing xterm sandbox.

Funny, the oringinal icon field (Icon=:resources/gnome-terminal) is replaced by (Icon=xterm)

