* detecting from command line
**********************
--net detected in pid_thread.cpp (strstr(pids[pid].cmd, "--net")), it might pick it up from the
params of the sandboxed program
--noroot detected in stats_dialog.cpp (strstr(cmd, "--noroot")), it might pick it up from the
params of the sandboxed program

